replies.body:
on the topic of the shield; 

it having a worse generation makes it a lot harder to generate shield with your Q. also losing W means you lost your means of consistently building it up, and E isn't really able to sustain the shield on its own.

the shield itself is bigger but Mordekaiser is mostly stacking health and movement items, so the shield is honestly a lot more fragile than it used to be pre-rework, where he was mostly going damage with health+resistances.
